title: Hem - Complete Discography (2000-2016)
description:
Info: Hem is a musical group from Brooklyn, New York. Their music has been variously described as "folk", "indie", "Americana" and "roots". Stylistically, their songs bridge 19th-century American parlour music, Appalachian folk music, gospel music, traditional American ballads, the European art song, early jazz and even contemporary classical music.

Includes:

2000 - Rabbit Songs
2002 - I'm Talking With My Mouth [EP]
2004 - Birds, Beasts, & Flowers [EP]
2004 - Eveningland
2006 - Funnel Cloud
2006 - No Word From Tom
2007 - Home Again, Home Again [EP]
2007 - Peace At Last [EP]
2009 - Twelfth Night
2013 - Departure and Farewell
2014 - The World is Outside [EP]
2016 - Better Days (New song)
